                        <interp inst="t18451124-name-661" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi>. I am landlord of this house—I ordered them all to produce their money on the Sunday morning—the prisoner produced some—among it was a sixpence which Knight identified—I took it all and gave it to the policeman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
